This avoids issues such as information asymmetry, elevated communication costs and low efficiency, which are common under other models of NPAs disposal. Quick Collection provides professional skip tracing, data desensitization, tools for debt collection and management, and collection strategy, as well as third-party payment on both sides of the platform. Quick Collection’s cloud-based platform is capable of handling 10,000 professionals working on the same time and it will fine-tune the debt collection and recovery processes, while our independently-developed proprietary algorithms can significantly reduce collection costs and improve debt recovery results.
